Reason:

Lowest architectural, SEO, and reputation risk.

Evidence:

Phoenix Founder Phase A Audit

Risk Assessment:

Low

Rollback Strategy:

Repository remains unchanged and can be reactivated at any time.

Approved By:

Project Owner

Status:

Implemented
